> missiles at Scorpina...
> ----- Original Message -----

{Scorpina}

    The fem bot would have grinned as her optics tracked and predicted the
course of the explosives ignoring the bullets that tore into her metal frame
work. Jumping up and forward she timed the explosions that rocked the earth
where she had been crouched to accelerate herself forward, riding the blasts
shock wave.

    As she flew forward towards the massive gesalt she transformed and
continued her journey forward towards Mobsters legs, claws extended ready to
find a firm hold, her tail cocking ready to jab forward the minute she
connected, the sharp point oozing green acid....
